OL,3,CAll GP surgeries in England to
OL,4,Cadvertise Jess's Rule to prevent
OL,5,Cavoidable deaths
OL,7,FJess's Rule, a system which calls for
OL,8,Ffamily doctors to think again if a
OL,9,Fpatient has had three appointments for
OL,10,Ftheir symptoms with no diagnosis, will
OL,11,Fbe advertised in all GP practices
OL,12,Facross England from this week.
OL,14,FThe rule is named after 27-year-old
OL,15,FJessica Brady, who contacted her
OL,16,Fsurgery 20 times before she passed
OL,17,Faway in 2020.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
