OL,4,Cadvertise Jess's Rule to prevent
OL,5,Cavoidable deaths
OL,7,FIt was rolled out in September to
OL,8,Fprevent avoidable deaths and help
OL,9,Fmedics avoid missing serious illnesses
OL,10,Fsuch as cancer.
OL,12,FJess's Rule urges GPs to think again
OL,13,Fwhen it comes to patients who have had
OL,14,Fthree appointments with no diagnosis,
OL,15,For if symptoms have worsened.
OL,17,FThey are encouraged to consider a
OL,18,Fsecond opinion, see patients face-to-
OL,19,Fface for physical examinations, or
OL,20,Forder more tests.
