OL,7,FMs Brady's mother Andrea Brady, said
OL,8,Fthe charity set up in her daughter's
OL,9,Fname has been "heartened" by the
OL,10,Fresponse from primary care to the
OL,11,F"three strikes and rethink" approach.
OL,13,FPosters advertising Jess's Rule have
OL,14,Fbeen distributed to all 6,170 GP
OL,15,Fpractices in England.
OL,17,FTheir display will boost patient
OL,18,Fsafety by urging family doctors to
OL,19,Fchallenge initial assumptions,
OL,20,Faccording to the Department of Health
OL,21,Fand Social Care.
