OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,8,F"Every patient deserves to be heard,
OL,9,Fand every serious illness deserves to
OL,10,Fbe caught early. Jess's Rule makes
OL,11,Fthat possible ` reminding clinicians
OL,12,Fto take a fresh look when symptoms
OL,13,Fpersist, and empowering patients to
OL,14,Fspeak up about their care.
OL,16,F"This is a fitting tribute to Jessica
OL,17,FBrady and the tireless campaigning of
OL,18,Fher parents. Their determination to
OL,19,Fturn tragedy into lasting change will
OL,20,Fhelp protect patients and save lives
OL,21,Ffor years to come."
