OL,7,FThe posters were co-designed by DHSC,
OL,8,FNHS England and Jess's parents Andrea
OL,9,Fand Simon Brady.
OL,11,FGP surgeries will also receive a
OL,12,Fletter from Mr Streeting and NHS
OL,13,FEngland's national medical director Dr
OL,14,FClaire Fuller to stress the importance
OL,15,Fof Jess's Rule.
