OL,7,FMs Brady, an engineer for Airbus,
OL,8,Fcontacted her GP surgery around 20
OL,9,Ftimes over six months in the lead up
OL,10,Fto her death in 2020, reporting
OL,11,Fsymptoms such as abdominal pain,
OL,12,Fcoughing, vomiting and weight loss.
OL,14,FDue to restrictions during the
OL,15,Fpandemic she was offered virtual
OL,16,Fappointments and prescribed
OL,17,Fmedications including antibiotics and
OL,18,Fsteroids. She was also told she may be
OL,19,Fsuffering from long Covid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
