OL,7,F"The Jessica Brady CEDAR Trust, the
OL,8,Fcharity established in Jess's name,
OL,9,Fhas been heartened by the response
OL,10,Ffrom primary care practitioners
OL,11,Fadopting 'the Three Strikes and We
OL,12,FRethink' approach.
OL,14,F"Many have committed to developing
OL,15,Ffurther training, while others have
OL,16,Fwritten to patients to endorse the
OL,17,Finitiative and show their support.
OL,18,FThis level of engagement has been
OL,19,Fprofoundly encouraging.
