OL,7,F"Jess's Rule posters have now been
OL,8,Fdistributed to all GP practices in
OL,9,FEngland and are expected to be
OL,10,Fdisplayed in consultation rooms. By
OL,11,Fsupporting clinicians to take a fresh
OL,12,Feyes approach when a patient returns
OL,13,Ffor a third time with the same or
OL,14,Fworsening symptoms, Jess's Rule aims
OL,15,Fto ensure serious illnesses, including
OL,16,Fcancer, are identified and treated
OL,17,Fearlier ` a goal I remain hopeful will
OL,18,Fbe achieved."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@MO]
