OL,7,FDr Fuller said: "Encouraging GP teams
OL,8,Fto challenge a diagnosis when it
OL,9,Fmatters most could save lives by
OL,10,Favoiding missed or late diagnoses, and
OL,11,FI'd like to thank Andrea and Simon
OL,12,FBrady and the Jessica Brady CEDAR
OL,13,FTrust for funding and providing their
OL,14,Fimportant insights to develop the
OL,15,Fposters."
