OL,7,FProfessor Victoria Tzortziou Brown,
OL,8,Fchairwoman of the Royal College of
OL,9,FGPs, said that Ms Brady's story "is an
OL,10,Fimportant reminder that sometimes a
OL,11,Frare diagnosis could be the right
OL,12,Fdiagnosis".
OL,14,FShe added: "Jess's Rule formalises
OL,15,F'best practice' in general practice
OL,16,Fand underlines the importance of
OL,17,Ftaking time to reflect and review a
OL,18,Fdiagnosis, if a treatment plan doesn't
OL,19,Fseem to be working.
