OL,7,F"This might mean having a more in-
OL,8,Fdepth conversation with the patient to
OL,9,Fsee what other factors could be
OL,10,Fimpacting their health, asking a
OL,11,Fcolleague for a second opinion, or if
OL,12,Fappropriate, making a referral to
OL,13,Fsecondary care.
OL,15,F"Timely diagnosis can mean better
OL,16,Foutcomes for patients ` but many
OL,17,Fserious conditions, including many
OL,18,Fcancers, are challenging to identify
OL,19,Fin primary care because the symptoms
OL,20,Fare often similar to other less
OL,21,Fserious and more common conditions.
