OL,7,F"The college has worked with Jess
OL,8,FBrady's family and the Jessica Brady
OL,9,FCEDAR Trust to develop learning
OL,10,Fresources for GPs on diagnosing cancer
OL,11,Fin younger people."
OL,13,FResearch by Nuffield Trust and the
OL,14,FHealth Foundation found that half of
OL,15,F16 to 24-year-olds required three or
OL,16,Fmore interactions with a GP surgery
OL,17,Fbefore being diagnosed with cancer,
OL,18,Fcompared with one-in-five across the
OL,19,Fpopulation.
